      "firm_id": "detailed_1",
      "description": "This vehicle is in fair condition and would make a reliable daily driver for someone who doesn't mind a few imperfections. The exterior has some visible sun fading on the hood and a few minor door dings, while the interior shows typical wear on the driver's seat and carpets. Mechanically, it runs and drives well, though it will likely need new tires and a brake service in the near future. It's a solid, honest car that has been regularly maintained but definitely shows its age.",
