    {
      "id": "sybil_11_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "sybil_11",
      "description": "Presenting a vehicle that exemplifies mechanical integrity and aesthetic appeal. This specimen has been rigorously maintained to ensure a refined driving experience and dependable performance. An exceptional opportunity for the discerning buyer seeking a sophisticated balance of luxury and long-term value.",
