    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_6",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Hey there! I\u2019m parting ways with my trusty ride, and honestly, she\u2019s been such a gem. It\u2019s in really solid shape and has plenty of life left for its next big adventure! I\u2019ve made sure to keep up with the basics so you can just hop in and go. If you're looking for something reliable that looks great and drives even better, you've found it!",
