    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_14_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_14",
      "description": "Available is a mechanically sound 2004 BMW M3 (E46), featuring the high-revving S54 3.2L inline-six engine equipped with individual throttle bodies and double VANOS variable valve timing. This example provides a visceral, linear power band and crisp throttle response. The 6-speed Getrag manual gearbox is paired with a factory M-Variable differential lock, ensuring precise torque distribution. Recent preventative maintenance includes a cooling system refresh and a comprehensive rear subframe reinforcement check. The suspension geometry remains true, offering the communicative feedback synonymous with this chassis. A well-sorted driver\u2019s car for the purist who values mechanical transparency and analog performance.",
